item.title: 【Cinema Center】MOVIE - The Out-Laws (1080p) (BluRay) (x265) (2023) [PeterChaser]
item.description:
Plot: Owen Browning, and his eccentric wife, cause a fair share of confusion by continually mislabeling their daughter-in-law, Parker, a yoga teacher, as a "stripper". Despite the perplexing humor and recurring jokes about orgies that miss their mark, the couple’s antics are merely the start of the surprises in store. As the wedding day approaches, Owen and his wife are introduced to Parker's unconventional parents, Billy and Lilly. Having lived off-grid throughout their daughter's relationship, the duo's eccentric lifestyle raises eyebrows. The plot takes a thrilling turn as Owen begins to suspect that Parker’s parents are the elusive Ghost Bandits, responsible for a series of crimes at his workplace. This bizarre revelation sets the stage for an unpredictable journey leading up to the big day.
Cast: Adam DeVine, Nina Dobrev, Ellen Barkin, Pierce Brosnan
Director: Tyler Spindel
Writer: Evan Turner, Ben Zazove
